stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idled : wanted = IDLE
    [*] --> Stowed : wanted = STOWED
    [*] --> Intaking : wanted = INTAKE [no cage]
    [*] --> Holding : wanted = INTAKE [cage detected]
    [*] --> Rejecting : wanted = REJECT
    [*] --> MovingToPosition : wanted = MOVE_TO_POSITION
    [*] --> IntakeAndMove : wanted = INTAKE_AND_MOVE
    [*] --> Homing : wanted = HOME
    [*] --> Holding : wanted = HOLD

    Intaking --> Holding : cage velocity drop detected
    Homing --> Idled : velocity below threshold for time period

    note right of Homing
        Drives carriage into hard stop.
        Resets position on completion.
    end note

    note right of Intaking
        Cage detection uses supply current
        and velocity thresholds
    end note

    note left of Idled
        Required before any other state
        unless homed via button tare
    end note
